# Local `wrangler dev` variables for the Charlotte On The Cheap connector.
# Copy to `.dev.vars` (gitignored) to override anything locally.
#
# There are NO credentials to set: the site is public and the connector's
# login page collects nothing. This file exists only so the base URL can be
# pointed elsewhere while developing.
COTC_BASE_URL=https://www.charlotteonthecheap.com
